  </sponsors>
  <source>Seoul National University Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted to evaluate the effectiveness of forced air warming using upper and
      lower body blankets by measuring core body temperature in patients undergoing video-assisted
      thoracic surgery in the lateral decubitus position over 2 hours of general anesthesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
